		<title>How to Leverage Profibus and Profinet for Troubleshooting and Preventing Downtime</title>
		<link>http://automation.isa.org/2017/01/how-to-leverage-profibus-and-profinet-for-troubleshooting-and-preventing-downtime/</link>
		<comments>http://automation.isa.org/2017/01/how-to-leverage-profibus-and-profinet-for-troubleshooting-and-preventing-downtime/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 16 Jan 2017 15:42:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[guest blogging for ISA]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[InTech]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[automation]]></category>
