<p><a href="https://uk.linkedin.com/in/martin-ross-1972205"><img class="alignleft wp-image-12860 size-full" src="https://i1.wp.com/automation.isa.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/48x48-linkedin.png?resize=48%2C48" alt="LinkedIn" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><strong><a href="mailto:martin.ross@honeywell.com"><img class="alignleft wp-image-12864 size-full" src="https://i1.wp.com/automation.isa.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/48x48-email.png?resize=48%2C48" alt="Email" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></strong></p>
